WEBVTT

00:00:01.180 --> 00:00:04.302
(Music)

00:00:04.302 --> 00:00:07.324
♪ It's all there in gospels ♪

00:00:07.324 --> 00:00:11.190
♪A Magdalene girl comes to pay her respects ♪

00:00:11.190 --> 00:00:12.910
♪ But her mind is awhirl ♪

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:15.278
♪ When she finds the tomb empty ♪

00:00:15.278 --> 00:00:17.456
♪ Straw had been rolled ♪

00:00:17.456 --> 00:00:19.185
♪ Not a sign of a corpse ♪

00:00:19.185 --> 00:00:21.016
♪ In the dark and the cold ♪

00:00:21.016 --> 00:00:23.192
♪ When she reaches the door ♪

00:00:23.192 --> 00:00:25.200
♪ Sees an unholy sight ♪

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:29.043
♪ There's a solitary figure and a halo of light ♪

00:00:29.043 --> 00:00:33.040
♪ He just carries on floating past Calvary Hill ♪